<p>Reenter the new password for confirmation.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Description</strong></p>
</div></div></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><div><div class="paragraph">
<p>The description is displayed within the information and settings for the calendar.</p>
</div></div></td>
</tr>
