</div>
</div>
</div><div class="sect1">
<h2 id="_creating_and_editing_appointments">4. Creating and editing appointments</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Proceed as described below to create, edit or delete appointments. Depending on your access rights, you might be able to create appointments for other users and edit their existing appointments.</p>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="_creating_an_appointment">4.1. Creating an appointment</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can only create appointments for users for which you have write permissions. You can not select users for which you do not have write permissions during creation of an appointment. Proceed as described below to create an appointment.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Creating an appointment:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Select a time or a time period. You can select a time by clicking on the field representing this particular point in time. Alternatively, you can select a time period by clicking and holding down the mouse button in the starting time field and then dragging the mouse to the ending time.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Pay attention to the explanations given in table 2 and carry out the settings as desired.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>save icon</strong> to save the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
